The People’s Democratic Party (PDP) has picked the former Minister of Women’s Affairs, Josephine Anenih, former Minister of Aviation, Osita Chidoka and governorship candidate of the party in the November election, Mr Valentine Ozigbo for zonal Congress committee of the party in Anambra State They are among the 14 -member zoning committee to oversee the party’s ward, local government and State Congresses scheduled for February 1- March 8,2022 in Anambra. This was made known by the State Publicity Secretary of PDP, Nnamdi Nwangwu Sunday in Awka. Also appointed in the committee were the party’s House of Assembly members, members of the House of Representatives and other stakeholders Nwangwu said that the appointment was sequel to a meeting of the caretaker committee at the party Secretariat, Udoka Housing Estate, Awka, Anambra State at the weekend - Advertisement -   ‘GAC has not settled for any replacement for…     Ogun politics after Buhari’s testimonials     ‘Dialogue, brute force will solve security challenges in…   He said Chairman of the party, Hon Ndubisi Nwobu at the meeting commended the National Working Committee led by His Excellency, Dr Iyorchia Ayu, for his able leadership of the party in the country He also, praised him for the confidence reposed in the State Leadership, while assuring the NWC of their unwavering loyalty and commitment to the project of Rebuilding and Rescuing Nigeria. “In consideration of the release of timetable and schedule of activities for the conduct of Wards, LGAs and State Congresses (February 1, 2022 – March 8, 2022) in adherence to the party constitution CAP 1(7)3c for equitable allocation of party offices, do hereby appoint the following members, to Zone all State Executive offices amongst the three Senatorial Zones. “Members of the zoning committee include: Iyom Barr Josephine Anenih – Chairman, former PDP National Woman Leader, former Minister of Women Affairs and Life member PDP BoT, Rt Hon Chukwuka Onyema – Member, former Minority Leader and Member House of Representatives, Mr Valentine Ozigbo – Member 2021 PDP Governorship Candidate Mrs Azuka Enemo – Member 2021 PDP Deputy Governorship Candidate and Hon Obinna Chidoka – Member, Current Member House of Reps. “Others are Hon Chinedu Onwuaso – Member, Current Member House of Reps, Hon Ebele Ejiofor – Member, Deputy Minority Leader Anambra State House of Assembly, Hon Noble Igwe – Member, Member Anambra State House of Assembly, Hon Johnbosco Akaegbobi -Member Anambra State House of Assembly “In the list are also, Lady Dr Rose Nwankwo – Member, Hon IK Obieke – Member, Hon Ossy Chinwuba – Member, former Member Anambra State House of Assembly, Sir Sam Ben Nwosu – Secretary and Hon Charles Ideli – Administrative Assistant.”